headline: Waters Corporation to Present at the Leerink Partners Global Healthcare Conference
summary: Waters Corporation (NYSE: WAT) announced that Udit Batra Ph.D., Waters President and Chief Executive Officer, will participate in a fireside chat at the Leerink Partners Global Healthcare Conference on Tuesday, March 11th, 2025 at 10:00AM Eastern Time.
